1 egg
1.5 cups milk


separate bowl
2 (300gcups flour
0.25 cups sugar 62 g
4 grams fine seasalt
1 g baking soda
12 g baking powder
whisk

mix flour mix with milky egg 
2 tbsp or 21 grams melted unsalted butter

whisk everything
rest batter for 5 minutes

medium heat
spray with oil and/or butter
cook 0.25 cups batter cook 2-3 minutes
Cook other side 1-2 minutes or until beautiful golden brown
